<!DOCTYPE html>

<html>
<head>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <link href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-BVYiiSIFeK1dGmJRAkycuHAHRg32OmUcww7on3RYdg4Va+PmSTsz/K68vbdEjh4u" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="~/css/styles.css" />
    <title>@ViewBag.Title</title>
</head>
<body>

        <div class="padding80 bgcolor-voilet">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <h2>It's time for a new adventure ! This is the place I was telling you about.</h2>
                        <p class="tmargin10">
                            Roam is a creative outlet for travellers, writers and photographers: to inspire readers to create and capture through words and photographs

                        </p>
                        <ul class="text-black tmargin40">
                            <li><span style="font-size: 15px" class="glyphicon glyphicon-cog"></span> Authentic places that I've visited</li>
                            <li><span style="font-size: 15px" class="glyphicon glyphicon-cog"></span> The World is a book and those who do not Travel read only one page</li>
                            <li><span style="font-size: 15px" class="glyphicon glyphicon-cog"></span>Always take the scenic route</li>
                        </ul>
                        <a href="" class="btn btn-default btn-round tmargin30">Read More</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <img class="img-responsive tmargin40" src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/154243/pexels-photo-154243.jpeg?w=1260&h=750&auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb" alt="Chania" width="560" height="445">

                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    <div class="container">
        @RenderBody()
    </div>

        
</body>
</html>
